game_description: In this game made by k3pt_vr on tiktok you get to hangout in various different maps. Every day you receive 100 of the games custom currency known as "cheddar". The point of the game is to have fun with others.

review_4: This game is great! Obviously it’s still in development so it’s gonna be a bit smaller but it’s definitely worth a try. I met the owner and he is such a cool guy!
